---

## 📈 Deliverable 5: Key Findings

| # | Finding |
|---|---------|
| 1 | Members take **82% more rides** than casuals |
| 2 | Casual rides are **63% longer** |
| 3 | Both prefer **electric bikes** (~65%) |
| 4 | Members peak on **weekdays morning rush** |
| 5 | Casuals peak on **weekends + afternoons** |
| 6 | Summer = 47% of casual rides (vs 36% for members) |
| 7 | Casuals start at **tourist spots** (Navy Pier) |
| 8 | Members start at **business districts** |

---

## 💡 Deliverable 6: Recommendations

### 1. "Summer Unlimited" Campaign 🎯
- **Why:** 47% of casual rides occur in summer
- **When:** Launch in May
- **How:** 20% discount + 1 week free trial
- **Expected Impact:** 15% conversion

### 2. Afternoon Rush Offer ⏰
- **Why:** 4-6 PM is casual peak
- **When:** Daily, 4-6 PM
- **How:** In-app "50% off first month"
- **Expected Impact:** 10% conversion

### 3. Free Electric Bike Trial 🚲
- **Why:** 65% of casuals use electric bikes
- **How:** 7-day free membership trial
- **Target:** Casuals who used electric 3+ times
- **Expected Impact:** 20% conversion

